metadata.name: Harmony Of Irony
metadata.description:
Even though life occasionally tears your heart to pieces, life will always be beautiful with its various plots that will never obey any souls. 

We can recognize happiness when we ever met sadness.
We can interpret a warm heart in the middle of cold days.
We can be grateful for success after we give a handshake into the hard moments in our life.
We can realize how precious a dim light is in the middle of the dark.
And maybe we can understand that there is always something blooming in every loss.


The balance of light and dark creates feelings for one another. 
Brings us to the bittersweet irony of life which slowly makes this journey like a colorful array in harmony. 

Harmony in the irony of life
